<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="advertize-v">advertize <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ædvətaɪz/    美 /'ædvərtaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(为...) 做广告 / 宣传；(为...) 登广告；征聘：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Now you are asked to make a poster to advertise a sporting event. 
现在要求你制作一幅海报，为一项体育赛事做广告。</p><footer>人教② – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should <strong>advertise for</strong> someone to look after the garden. 
我们该登个广告聘人来照管花园。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>advertising / advertizing  // n [U]  </p></div>